i# 打包流程		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i虽然你可		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i以[直接调用 Nix 包管理器内置的 `builtins.derivation` 函数进行打包](https://scrive.github.io/nix-workshop/04-derivations/04-raw-derivation.html)，		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i但我们一般用更为方便的 `stdenv.mkDerivation` 函数来生成一个 Nix 包管理		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i器的打包定义。相比于 `builtins.derivation`，`stdenv.mkDerivation` 将打		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i包过程分成了 7 个步骤（Phase）：		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i1. 解压（Unpack phase）		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i   - 在这一步中，`stdenv.mkDerivation` 会自动解压 `src` 参数指定的源码		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i     包。例如如果你的源码包是 `.tar.gz` 格式的，就会自动调用		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i     `tar xf`。		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i   - 但 `stdenv.mkDerivation` 不能识别所有压缩格式，例如 `.zip` 就不行		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i     ，需要手动指定解压命令：		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i     ```nix		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i     nativeBuildInputs = [ unzip ];		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i     unpackPhase = ''		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i       unzip $src		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i     '';		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i     ```		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i   - `stdenv.mkDerivation` 要求源码包的顶层是一个文件夹，解压完成后会		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i     自动 `cd` 进去。		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i2. 打补丁（Patch phase）		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i   - 在这一步中，`stdenv.mkDerivation` 会按顺序应用 `patches` 列表中的		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i     所有补丁。这一步可以用来解决一部分软件和 NixOS 的不兼容问题。		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i3. 配置（Configure phase）		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i   - 这一步相当于运行 `./configure` 或者		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i     `cmake`。`stdenv.mkDerivation` 会自动检测打包方案并调用相应命令，		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
